==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Iridescent
<hw>Ir`i*des"cent</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>iris</ets>, <ets>iridis</ets>, the rainbow: cf. F.
<ets>iridescent</ets>.]</ety> <def>Having colors like the rainbow;
exhibiting a play of changeable colors; nacreous; prismatic; <as>as,
<ex>iridescent</ex> glass</as>. See <er>iridescence</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Iridian</ent>⟦br⟧
